@endpoint POST /accounts/{accountId}/plans/addons
@desc Subscribe additional plan
@required {accountId: str # The account ID.}
@returns(201) Account plans updated.
@errors {400: **HTTP Status Code:** `400`<br>
**Error Code:** `2100`<br> 
This sub account is on self pay mode.<br>
Cannot update Additional plan for a sub account under free plan.<br>
Additional Zoom Rooms plan cannot be added to a sub account that already has a Zoom Rooms base plan.<br>
This sub account already has the additional plan: {planCode}.<br>
Master accounts with bulk licenses cannot provision, update, or cancel plans for sub accounts using APIs, please use the billing portal or contact Support., 404: **HTTP Status Code:** `404`<br>
**Error Code:** `1001`<br> 
User does not exist.<br>
**Error Code:** `2001`<br> 
Account does not exist: {subAccountId}.
}

@endpoint PUT /accounts/{accountId}/plans/addons
@desc Update an additional plan
@required {accountId: str # The account ID., hosts: int # Number of hosts for this plan., type: str # Account <a href="https://marketplace.zoom.us/docs/api-reference/other-references/plans">plan type.</a>}
@returns(200) **Error Code:** `200`<br>
Free trial and VIP accounts can't update sub plans.<br>
You don’t have subscription for ({oldPlanCode}) yet.

@returns(204) **HTTP Status Code:** `204`<br>
Additional plan updated for the account.
@errors {300: **Error Code:** `300`<br>
Plan types do not match, oldPlanType: {oldPlanType} newPlanType: {newPlanType}., 400: **HTTP Status Code:** `400`<br>
**Error Code:** `2100`
<br>This sub account is on self pay mode.
<br>Invalid Additional Plan Type: {newPlanCode}.
