@optional {page_size: int=30 # The number of records returned within a single API call., next_page_token: str # The next page token is used to paginate through large result sets. A next page token will be returned whenever the set of available results exceeds the current page size. The expiration period for this token is 15 minutes.}
@returns(200) **HTTP Status Code:** `200` <br>
Archived IM chat messages returned.
@errors {300: **Error Code:**`300` <br>
The next page token is either invalid or has expired.<br>
Report requested exceeds 6 month limit.}

