GISTER requests. Note that if you are using the UDP transport protocol, the default port is 5060. If you are using UDP with a different port number, that port number must be included with the IP address., user_name: str # The phone number associated with the user in the SIP account., voice_mail: str # The number to dial for checking voicemail.}
@optional {registration_expire_time: int=60 # The number of minutes after which the SIP registration of the Zoom client user will expire, and the client will auto register to the SIP server., transport_protocol: str(UDP/TCP/TLS/AUTO) # Protocols supported by the SIP provider.<br> The value must be either `UDP`, `TCP`, `TLS`, `AUTO`., transport_protocol2: str(UDP/TCP/TLS/AUTO) # Protocols supported by the SIP provider.<br> The value must be either `UDP`, `TCP`, `TLS`, `AUTO`., transport_protocol3: str(UDP/TCP/TLS/AUTO) # Protocols supported by the SIP provider.<br> The value must be either `UDP`, `TCP`, `TLS`, `AUTO`.}
@returns(200) **Error Code:** `200`<br>
