This error is thrown if you added a user in your account but the user did not accept the invitation on time and the invitation expired - thus making the userId invalid., 404: **HTTP Status Code:** `404` **Not Found**<br><br>
**Error Code:** `1001`<br>
User does not exist: $userId.}

